    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This silver band is cast to resemble a pack of hunting wolves. On command, the wearer can gain the scent ability with a range of 10 feet (20 feet upwind, 5 feet downwind) as the wolf aspect of the hunter's animal focus class feature. If the wearer is a hunter with that aspect, this headband instead increases the wearer's effective hunter level for the wolf aspect by 8 levels.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, bloodhoundAPG, creator must have the animal focus class feature</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Advanced Class Guide",
